    <!--**
    ** Plain text description of the change
    ** Extracted from git commit messages
    **-->
    <Description>
      The definition for shared library symbol export macros was
      previously only definied in itkWin32Header.h for DLL creation. However, support was
      added to GCC visibility, so the ITK_EXPORT macro definition was moved to itkMacro.h.
    </Description>

    <!--**
    ** Sample code snippets
    ** Extracted from git diff of changed files in Examples and Testing
    **-->
    <SampleCode>
      <Old>
        <![CDATA[
        #include "itkWin32Header.h"

        class ITK_EXPORT Gene
        {
        ]]>
      </Old>

      <New>
        <![CDATA[
        #include "itkMacro.h"

        class ITK_EXPORT Gene
        ]]>
      </New>

    </SampleCode>

    <!--**
